greetings to chairman of South Korean's parliament. Mr. Chong 
Chae-mun shared the same views with his host. He expressed his 
wish for continuing the development of friendship and 
cooperation between the two countries, that will contribute to 
the maintaining of peace, stability devlopment and prosperity in 
the region and the world as whole. 

