  [Text] According to Seoul radio, the nation-selling Kim 
Yong-sam traitorous clique proclaimed [kongpo] on 6 May that the 
puppet Army, Navy, and Air Force will stage a joint tactical 
exercise for the first half of the year, a new large-scale war 
