ground, in the air, and in the sea -- including a battle 
exercise; a chemical, biological, and radiological war exercise; 
an exercise on transporting troops and equipment; and a takeoff 
and landing exercise on emergency airstrips -- in the north of 
Kyonggi Province near the Military Demarcation Line [MDL], South 
Kyongsang Province, and the West Sea of South Korea. The puppet 
clique is also planning to mobilize many domestic reserve troops 
for this war exercise. 
  The U.S. imperialists and South Korean puppets should think 
deeply about the grave consequences as a result of their 
criminal act of driving the situation on the Korean peninsula to 
the brink of war by repeating armed reinforcement and war 
exercises. 

