BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, May 7 (KCNA) -- The dear leader Comrade 
Kim Chong-il sent a centenary birthday table to Kim Chang-yong 
residing in Onchon-up, Onchon County, South Pyongan Province. 
The birthday table was conveyed to her on May 6. 
  Born into a poor peasant family in the declining days of the 
feudal society of the ri dynasty, she was subjected to all sorts 
