During the fatherland liberation war she took an active part in 
the struggle for wartime food grain production and aided the 
People's Army both materially and morally. In the postwar 
period, too, she did her everything for the prosperity of the 
socialist homeland. 
  Now, she has a big family of more than 30. 
  In the Democratic People's Republic of Korea today the 
number 
of those who enjoy longevity is on a steady increase thanks to 
popular policies. 

</TEXT>

