<H3> <TI>   Five Politburo CPP-NPA-NDF Members Arrested </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Five Politburo CPP-NPA-NDF Members Arrested </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK0505081994 Quezon City PTV-4 Television Network in Tagalog 
0500 GMT 5 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0505081994 </F>
<F P=104>  Quezon City PTV-4 Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Tagalog </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Five top leaders of CPP-NPA-NDF [Communist Party of 
the Philippines-New People's Army-National Democratic Front] 
fell into the hands of the military authorities of Bulacan PNP 
[Philippine National Police] Command, Recom [Regional Command] 
III Intelligence and PNP Intelligence Command, after they were 
arrested on their way to a meeting in Barangay [village] 
