  Those arrested were identified as Wilma Austria-Tiamzon 
alias 
Comrade Rhea, Eugenia Magbantay-Kabaso and her sister Caridad 
Magbantay-Pascual alias Caring, Luisito de la Cruz alias Ted or 
Janus and Gerry Rato: all ranking members of executive committee 
or the Politburo of Central Luzon Regional Party Committee of 
CPP-NPA-NDF. The five are presently under the custody of 
Bulacan PNP headquarters and are scheduled to be brought to Camp 
Crame at 3 o'clock this afternoon. 

