  [Text] Seoul, May 8 (YONHAP) -- The South Korean Foreign 
Ministry praised dismissal of Japanese Justice Minister Shigeto 
Nagano Sunday, calling it "appropriate" for building new South 
Korea-Japan relations. 
  "The dismissal of Minister Nagano was the result of Prime 
Minister Tsutomu Hata's determination and courage," a Ministry 
