<H3> <TI>   Government Decision Said Imminent </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Government Decision Said Imminent </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK0905071594 Seoul YONHAP in English 0708 GMT 9 May 94 </F>
