<F P=100> Vietnam </F>
<H3> <TI>   Tuyen Quang Electricity Authority's Achievement Noted </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Tuyen Quang Electricity Authority's Achievement Noted </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK0705093994 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 
1430 GMT 4 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0705093994 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network </F>
<F P=105>  Vietnamese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Since early this year, the Tuyen Quang Province 
Electricity Authority has made considerable investment in 
building many rural electrification projects to support 
production and the daily activities of the local multiethnic 
compatriots. Thanks to its good preparations in material, 
means, and manpower, the electricity authority has completed a 
35-kilovolt transformer station and the Tuyen Quang-Ham Yen 
powerline ahead of schedule in order to channel electricity 
promptly from the national power grid to serve the multiethnic 
compatriots of Ham Yen. 
  At present, the provincial electricity authority is 
concentrating its capital, cadres, engineers, and means on 
completing the construction of the Tuyen Quang-Son Duong and Ham 
Yen-Chien Hoa powerlines and their supporting 35-kilovolt 
transformer stations in time to celebrate this year's National 
Day. 

</TEXT>

