<H3> <TI>   Denies Daily's Dismissal Report </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Denies Daily's Dismissal Report </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK1005061294 Bangkok BANGKOK POST (INSIDE INDOCHINA 
Supplement) in English 10 May 94 p 2 </F>

<F P=103> BK1005061294 </F>
<F P=104>  Bangkok BANGKOK POST (INSIDE INDOCHINA 
